sg.edu.cs2103aug2015_w13_2j

Class IntegrationTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • sg.edu.cs2103aug2015_w13_2j.IntegrationTests

  • public class IntegrationTests
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains tests for testing all components to ensure they work together to produce expected output Includes tests for the synchronization of the components Tests 4 components Logic, UI, Parser and Storage as a whole. Mimics a user's action of adding a command into the application by calling executeCommand() in Logic and examines the output produced by the User Interface Stub after the whole operation. Before any tests are carried out, the file will be cleared so that individual tests do not affect each other
    Author:
    Nguyen Tuong Van
